## Editorial Standards and Quality Assurance

Consistency:
- Standardize article numbering, spelling, and nomenclature (e.g., “Lok Sabha”, “Rajya Sabha”, “Council of Ministers”).
- Use uniform templates for question stems, answer explanations, and source annotations.

Legal accuracy:
- Cross-check each question against primary constitutional texts and official portals.
- Triangulate procedural rules (e.g., joint sitting) with parliamentary documentation.
- For case references, rely on official summaries and institutional explainers; avoid disputed characterizations.

Coverage completeness:
- Ensure balanced representation across topics and cognitive levels.
- Include scenario-based questions that require multi-step reasoning and article linkage.

Quality assurance steps:
- Three-pass review: legal accuracy, procedural clarity, and pedagogy alignment.
- Final audit checklist confirming article mapping, source integrity, and ambiguity reduction.

Table 24. QA checklist

| Criterion | Checkpoint |
|---|---|
| Article accuracy | All article references verified against official texts |
| Procedural correctness | Bills, emergencies, impeachment—steps and exceptions aligned |
| Source integrity | Each answer cites at least one primary and one secondary source |
| Pedagogical clarity | Questions avoid ambiguity; stems match cognitive level |
| Balance and completeness | Topic coverage and difficulty distribution meet plan |
| Amendment linkage | Significant amendments integrated where relevant |
| Case referencing | Only official summaries or credible explainers used; holdings precisely stated |

## Conclusion

This blueprint equips editors and researchers to compile a rigorous 200-question compendium on the Union Government of India. It provides a structured architecture of the executive, Parliament, Supreme Court, federal relations, and emergency provisions, with procedural tables, jurisdiction matrices, and finance devolution summaries. The question design schema ensures balanced coverage and depth, while editorial and QA standards maintain accuracy and pedagogical clarity. By anchoring every question in constitutional articles and credible sources, the compendium will support advanced exam preparation and applied constitutional reasoning.

